					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm gonna stay neutral with this one. I mean I dislike fart jokes, but that audio file was the best. It made me smile.</p> <p>Who collaborated with you on this Sal?</p> <p>Also:</p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-7394-J is small tree frog (species unknown) with the ability to [DATA EXPUNGED], causing massive internal bleeding and psychological trauma in subjects caught within a 2 kilometer radius of SCP-7394-J. Approximately 259 deaths have been traced back to SCP-7394-J.</p> </blockquote> <p>I don't really see what this whole paragraph being needed. The rest of the description is fine, but I'm not sure how this contributes to the article :/</p> 
				 	]]>
